    "One of our proposed methods extends HITS while maximizing prior knowledge about accounts to produce accurate credibility scores.",
    "The intuition is that misinformation sharers are hubs leading to unreliable news sources, and vice versa.Machine learning methods have been employed to classify social media accounts based on their credibility.",
